===Noun===
#In [[music]], the '''complement''' of any [[interval]] is the interval with which it spans an [[octave]]. For any [[pitch class]], 1-11, the complement is its [[inversion]].
#In [[music]], the '''complement''' of any [[set]] of [[pitch class]]es is the remainder of the [[full chromatic]].
:(DeLone et. al. (Eds.), 1975, chap. 6)

